### CREATING TRANSACTIONS
USE sql_store;

START TRANSACTION;

INSERT INTO orders (customer_id, order_date, status)
VALUES (1, '2019-01-01', 1);

INSERT INTO order_items
VALUES (LAST_INSERT_ID(), 1, 1, 1);

COMMIT;

### CONCURRENCY and LOCKING
## CONCURRENCY Problems
--Lost Updates
--Dirty Reads (事务 A 被 B 虚晃一枪，B 更新后又撤回，中间状态被 A 读取）
  解决方案：隔离 Isolation，READ COMMITTED
--None Repeating Reads
  解决方案：Repeatable Reads, Isolation
--Phantom Reads
  解决方案：SERIALIZABLE 序列化

### Transaction Isolation Levels
## 不同的隔离等级定义
1.Read Uncommitted 
2.Read Committed
3.Repeatable read
4.Serializable
1-->4, 上锁更多，解决/避免的问题更多，同时资源消耗更多。
mySQL 默认为 Level3 Repeatable read.

## 如何设置不同的隔离等级
SHOW VARIABLES LIKE 'transaction_isolation';
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL SERIALIZABLE; 
SET  SESSION TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL SERIALIZABLE; //仅设置未来的事件隔离等级
SET GLOBAL TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL SERIALIZABLE;  //设置所有的事件隔离等级

